<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Estadística — Grado 11°</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,700;0,900;1,400&family=Source+Sans+3:wght@300;400;600;700&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root{
  --ink:#0f0e0c;--cream:#faf7f2;--amber:#c8790a;--amber-l:#f5c842;
  --teal:#0b6464;--teal-l:#1a8f8f;--rose:#b03026;
  --slate:#253245;--muted:#7a7570;--border:#d8d0c4;
  --card:#fff;--shadow:rgba(15,14,12,.08);--sec:#f0ebe0;
}
*,*::before,*::after{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
html{scroll-behavior:smooth}
body{font-family:'Source Sans 3',sans-serif;background:var(--cream);color:var(--ink);line-height:1.75;font-size:16px}

header{background:var(--ink);color:var(--cream);padding:54px 40px 44px;text-align:center;position:relative;overflow:hidden}
header::before{content:'';position:absolute;inset:0;background:repeating-linear-gradient(45deg,transparent,transparent 48px,rgba(200,121,10,.05) 48px,rgba(200,121,10,.05) 49px)}
header h1{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:clamp(2.4rem,5vw,4rem);font-weight:900;letter-spacing:-1px;position:relative;line-height:1.1}
header h1 em{color:var(--amber-l);font-style:italic}
header .sub{font-size:1rem;color:rgba(250,247,242,.6);margin-top:10px;position:relative;letter-spacing:.04em;text-transform:uppercase}
.badge-row{display:flex;justify-content:center;gap:10px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:18px;position:relative}
.badge{background:rgba(200,121,10,.18);border:1px solid rgba(200,121,10,.4);color:var(--amber-l);font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:.72rem;padding:4px 13px;border-radius:2px;letter-spacing:.06em}

nav{background:var(--slate);position:sticky;top:0;z-index:100;overflow-x:auto;white-space:nowrap;border-bottom:3px solid var(--amber)}
nav a{display:inline-block;color:rgba(250,247,242,.75);text-decoration:none;font-size:.8rem;font-weight:600;padding:13px 16px;transition:all .2s;letter-spacing:.04em;text-transform:uppercase}
nav a:hover,nav a.active{color:var(--amber-l);background:rgba(200,121,10,.12)}
nav .n{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:.68rem;opacity:.5;margin-right:4px}

.container{max-width:1100px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 24px}
section{padding:68px 0}
section:nth-child(even){background:var(--sec)}
.sec-head{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:18px;margin-bottom:40px}
.sec-head .nn{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:3.8rem;font-weight:900;color:var(--border);line-height:1}
.sec-head h2{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:1.9rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--ink)}
.sec-head p{color:var(--muted);font-size:.9rem;margin-top:2px}
.divider{width:44px;height:4px;background:var(--amber);margin:10px 0}

.card{background:var(--card);border-radius:4px;border:1px solid var(--border);padding:26px 30px;margin-bottom:18px;box-shadow:0 2px 10px var(--shadow)}
.card h3{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:1.25rem;color:var(--slate);margin-bottom:10px}
.card.hl{border-left:4px solid var(--amber);background:linear-gradient(135deg,#fffdf5,#fff)}
.card.tl{border-left:4px solid var(--teal)}
.card.rs{border-left:4px solid var(--rose)}
.def-box{background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--slate),#1a2b3e);color:var(--cream);border-radius:4px;padding:22px 26px;margin:18px 0}
.def-box h4{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;color:var(--amber-l);margin-bottom:8px;font-size:1.05rem}
.def-box p{font-size:.93rem;opacity:.9;line-height:1.6}

.ex{background:#fffdf3;border:1px solid #e8c870;border-radius:4px;padding:22px 26px;margin:18px 0}
.ex-hd{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;margin-bottom:14px}
.ex-hd .etag{background:var(--amber);color:var(--ink);font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:.7rem;font-weight:600;padding:3px 10px;border-radius:2px}
.ex-hd h4{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:1rem;color:var(--slate)}
.step{display:flex;gap:12px;margin:9px 0}
.sn{width:26px;height:26px;background:var(--teal);color:#fff;border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:.72rem;font-weight:600;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:3px}
.sc{flex:1}
.sc b{color:var(--teal);display:block;font-size:.82rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.04em;margin-bottom:2px}

.tw{overflow-x:auto;margin:18px 0}
table{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;font-size:.88rem}
thead{background:var(--slate);color:#fff}
thead th{padding:11px 14px;text-align:left;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:.77rem;letter-spacing:.04em}
tbody tr:nth-child(even){background:var(--sec)}
tbody td{padding:9px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border)}
tbody tr:hover{background:#fff8e6}
tfoot td{padding:9px 14px;background:var(--ink);color:var(--amber-l);font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:.82rem;font-weight:600}

.fm{background:var(--ink);color:var(--amber-l);font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;padding:14px 18px;border-radius:4px;margin:12px 0;font-size:.95rem;text-align:center}
.fm small{color:rgba(245,200,66,.55);font-size:.72rem;display:block;margin-top:3px}

.g2{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(280px,1fr));gap:18px}
.g3{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(210px,1fr));gap:18px}

.inp{border:2px solid var(--border);border-radius:4px;padding:9px 13px;font-size:.95rem;font-family:'Source Sans 3',sans-serif;outline:none;transition:border-color .2s;width:100%}
.inp:focus{border-color:var(--teal)}
.inp-sm{width:140px!important}
.lbl{font-size:.82rem;color:var(--muted);font-weight:600;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.04em;display:block;margin-bottom:4px}
.row{display:flex;gap:12px;align-items:flex-end;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:12px}
.btn{background:var(--teal);color:#fff;border:none;border-radius:4px;padding:10px 22px;font-family:'Source Sans 3',sans-serif;font-size:.93rem;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;transition:all .2s}
.btn:hover{background:var(--teal-l);transform:translateY(-1px)}
.btn.am{background:var(--amber)}.btn.am:hover{background:#e08a0c}
.btn.rs{background:var(--rose)}.btn.rs:hover{background:#c83228}
.btn.dk{background:var(--slate)}.btn.dk:hover{background:#1a2b3e}
.res-box{background:var(--sec);border-left:4px solid var(--teal);padding:13px 17px;border-radius:0 4px 4px 0;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:1rem;color:var(--slate);min-height:46px;margin-top:10px}

.ch{background:#fff;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:4px;padding:22px;margin:18px 0}
.ch h4{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;color:var(--slate);margin-bottom:14px;font-size:1.05rem}

.act{background:#fff;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:4px;padding:30px;margin-bottom:22px}
.act-hd{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;margin-bottom:18px}
.act-num{background:var(--rose);color:#fff;width:42px;height:42px;border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:1.15rem;font-weight:700;flex-shrink:0}
.act-hd h3{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:1.35rem;color:var(--slate)}
.q-area{background:var(--sec);border-radius:4px;padding:18px 22px;margin:14px 0;border-left:4px solid var(--amber)}
.q-area p{margin-bottom:6px}
.opts label{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:9px;padding:7px 11px;border-radius:4px;cursor:pointer;margin-bottom:5px;transition:background .15s}
.opts label:hover{background:rgba(11,100,100,.07)}
.opts input[type=radio]{margin-top:4px;accent-color:var(--teal);flex-shrink:0}
.fb{padding:11px 15px;border-radius:4px;margin-top:10px;font-weight:600;font-size:.9rem;display:none}
.fb.ok{background:#d4edda;border:1px solid #28a745;color:#155724}
.fb.no{background:#f8d7da;border:1px solid #dc3545;color:#721c24}

/* SCI CALC */
.sci{background:#111;border-radius:8px;padding:14px;margin:12px 0;display:none}
.sci.open{display:block}
.sdisp{background:#000;padding:10px;border-radius:4px;text-align:right;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;margin-bottom:10px}
.sdisp .sexp{color:#555;font-size:.73rem;min-height:18px}
.sdisp .sval{color:var(--amber-l);font-size:1.55rem;font-weight:600;word-break:break-all}
.sbg{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(6,1fr);gap:5px}
.sb{background:#1e1e1e;border:1px solid #2e2e2e;color:#ccc;padding:9px 3px;border-radius:3px;cursor:pointer;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:.73rem;font-weight:600;transition:background .1s;text-align:center}
.sb:hover{background:#2a2a2a}.sb.fn{color:#99ccff;background:#0a1525}.sb.op{color:#ffcc66;background:#1a1500}
.sb.eq{background:var(--amber);color:#111;grid-column:span 2}.sb.cl{color:#ff8080;background:#1a0000}
.tog-c{background:var(--ink);color:var(--amber-l);border:1px solid #555;border-radius:4px;padding:6px 14px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:.78rem;cursor:pointer;margin-bottom:8px}

.pgbar{height:6px;background:var(--border);border-radius:3px;overflow:hidden;margin:6px 0}
.pgfill{height:100%;background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--teal),var(--amber));border-radius:3px;transition:width .4s}

/* MODAL / OVERLAYS */
.overlay{position:fixed;inset:0;background:rgba(15,14,12,.88);z-index:500;display:none;align-items:center;justify-content:center;padding:16px}
.overlay.show{display:flex}
.modal-box{background:var(--cream);border-radius:6px;max-width:520px;width:100%;position:relative;box-shadow:0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,.4);padding:40px}
.modal-box h2{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:1.6rem;color:var(--slate);margin-bottom:8px}
.modal-box p{color:var(--muted);font-size:.92rem;margin-bottom:20px}

/* CODE SCREEN */
.code-screen{position:fixed;inset:0;background:var(--ink);z-index:400;display:none;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;justify-content:center;padding:32px}
.code-screen.show{display:flex}
.code-screen h2{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:2.2rem;color:var(--amber-l);margin-bottom:6px;text-align:center}
.code-screen > p{color:rgba(250,247,242,.6);margin-bottom:28px;text-align:center;font-size:.95rem}
.code-in{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:2rem;letter-spacing:.3em;text-align:center;background:rgba(255,255,255,.07);border:2px solid rgba(200,121,10,.4);color:var(--amber-l);border-radius:6px;padding:18px 28px;width:220px;outline:none;margin-bottom:14px}
.code-in:focus{border-color:var(--amber)}
.code-error{color:#ff8080;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:.85rem;margin-bottom:14px;display:none}

/* TEST */
.test-wrap{border:2px solid var(--ink);border-radius:6px;overflow:hidden;background:var(--cream)}
.test-top{background:var(--ink);color:var(--cream);padding:26px 30px}
.test-top h2{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:1.6rem}
.test-top p{opacity:.65;font-size:.9rem;margin-top:5px}
.test-meta{display:flex;gap:16px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:14px}
.tm{background:rgba(255,255,255,.1);padding:6px 14px;border-radius:2px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:.78rem}
.test-body{padding:28px}
.iq{border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);padding:22px 0}
.iq:last-child{border-bottom:none}
.iq .qn{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:.72rem;color:var(--amber);font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.06em;margin-bottom:4px}
.iq .qc{font-size:.76rem;color:var(--muted);font-style:italic;margin-bottom:7px}
.iq .qt{color:var(--slate);margin-bottom:13px;line-height:1.7}
.io{display:flex;gap:11px;align-items:flex-start;padding:7px 11px;border-radius:4px;cursor:pointer;margin-bottom:4px;transition:background .15s}
.io:hover{background:#f0fafa}.io input{margin-top:4px;accent-color:var(--teal);flex-shrink:0}
.test-foot{background:var(--sec);border-top:2px solid var(--border);padding:18px 28px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:14px}
.timer-disp{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:1.3rem;color:var(--rose);font-weight:600}

/* STU FORM */
.stu-form{background:#f8f4ee;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:4px;padding:24px;margin-bottom:20px}
.stu-form h3{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:1.2rem;color:var(--slate);margin-bottom:8px}
.form-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(240px,1fr));gap:14px;margin-bottom:14px}
select.inp{background:#fff;cursor:pointer}

/* TEACHER PANEL */
.tpanel{position:fixed;inset:0;background:var(--ink);z-index:600;overflow-y:auto;padding:40px;display:none}
.tpanel.show{display:block}
.tpanel h2{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:2rem;margin-bottom:6px;color:var(--amber-l)}
.tpanel > p{opacity:.6;margin-bottom:28px}
.stat-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(160px,1fr));gap:14px;margin-bottom:28px}
.stat-box{background:rgba(255,255,255,.06);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.1);border-radius:4px;padding:18px;text-align:center}
.stat-box .val{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:2rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--amber-l)}
.stat-box .lbl2{font-size:.78rem;opacity:.6;margin-top:4px;letter-spacing:.04em;text-transform:uppercase}
.tpanel table thead{background:rgba(255,255,255,.12)}
.tpanel table thead th{color:var(--amber-l)}
.tpanel table tbody td{color:rgba(250,247,242,.85);border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.07)}
.tpanel table tbody tr:nth-child(even){background:rgba(255,255,255,.04)}
.tpanel table tbody tr:hover{background:rgba(200,121,10,.12)}

/* TEACHER ACCESS MODAL */
.ta-modal{position:fixed;inset:0;background:rgba(0,0,0,.9);z-index:700;display:none;align-items:center;justify-content:center}
.ta-modal.show{display:flex}
.ta-box{background:var(--ink);border:1px solid rgba(200,121,10,.3);border-radius:8px;padding:40px;max-width:380px;width:90%;text-align:center}
.ta-box h2{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;color:var(--amber-l);font-size:1.5rem;margin-bottom:8px}
.ta-box p{color:rgba(250,247,242,.6);font-size:.9rem;margin-bottom:22px}
.ta-in{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:1.3rem;letter-spacing:.2em;text-align:center;background:rgba(255,255,255,.07);border:2px solid rgba(200,121,10,.3);color:var(--amber-l);border-radius:6px;padding:14px;width:100%;outline:none;margin-bottom:12px}
.ta-in:focus{border-color:var(--amber)}
.ta-error{color:#ff8080;font-size:.83rem;margin-bottom:12px;display:none;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace}

/* RESULT HIGHLIGHT */
.res-hi-ok{background:#d4edda!important}
.res-hi-no{background:#f8d7da!important}
.exp-note{background:#fff3cd;border:1px solid #e0a800;border-radius:4px;padding:9px 13px;margin-top:8px;font-size:.85rem;color:#664d03}


/* EXAM ACTIVE MODE — hide all page content */
body.exam-active > header,
body.exam-active > nav,
body.exam-active > section,
body.exam-active > footer {display:none!important}
body.exam-active .code-screen{display:none!important}

/* Warning modal */
.warn-modal{position:fixed;inset:0;background:rgba(0,0,0,.92);z-index:900;display:none;align-items:center;justify-content:center;padding:20px}
.warn-modal.show{display:flex}
.warn-box{background:#fff;border-radius:8px;padding:36px;max-width:460px;width:100%;text-align:center;box-shadow:0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,.5)}
.warn-box h2{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:1.5rem;color:#b03026;margin-bottom:10px}
.warn-box p{color:#444;font-size:.95rem;margin-bottom:22px;line-height:1.6}
.warn-box .wb{display:flex;gap:12px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap}

/* Exam overlay full-screen during exam */
#testOverlay.exam-mode{z-index:800;background:var(--cream)}
#testOverlay.exam-mode > div{max-height:100vh;border-radius:0;max-width:100%}

/* Sending spinner */
.send-spinner{display:inline-block;width:18px;height:18px;border:3px solid rgba(255,255,255,.3);border-top-color:#fff;border-radius:50%;animation:spin .7s linear infinite;vertical-align:middle;margin-right:8px}
@keyframes spin{to{transform:rotate(360deg)}}

@media(max-width:640px){
  .sec-head .nn{font-size:2.4rem}
  .sec-head h2{font-size:1.3rem}
  header{padding:36px 18px}
  section{padding:48px 0}
  .card{padding:18px}
  .test-body{padding:16px}
  .sbg{grid-template-columns:repeat(5,1fr)}
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- ═══ TEACHER ACCESS MODAL ═══ -->
<div class="ta-modal" id="taModal">
  <div class="ta-box">
    <h2>🔐 Panel Docente</h2>
    <p>Ingresa la contraseña de acceso</p>
    <input class="ta-in" id="taIn" type="password" maxlength="20" placeholder="••••••••" onkeydown="if(event.key==='Enter')verifyTeacher()">
    <div class="ta-error" id="taErr">Contraseña incorrecta.</div>
    <button class="btn am" style="width:100%;margin-bottom:10px" onclick="verifyTeacher()">Ingresar</button>
    <button style="background:none;border:none;color:rgba(250,247,242,.3);font-size:.82rem;cursor:pointer" onclick="document.getElementById('taModal').classList.remove('show')">Cancelar</button>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ═══ TEACHER PANEL ═══ -->
<div class="tpanel" id="teacherPanel">
  <button class="btn rs" style="margin-bottom:24px" onclick="closePanel()">✕ Cerrar panel</button>
  <h2>📊 Panel del Docente — Estadística Grado 11°</h2>
  <p>Resultados registrados en este navegador</p>
  <div class="stat-grid" id="panelStats"></div>
  <div id="panelTableWrap"></div>
  <div style="display:flex;gap:12px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:24px">
    <button class="btn am" onclick="exportExcel()">📥 Descargar Excel</button>
    <button class="btn rs" onclick="clearResults()">🗑 Limpiar resultados</button>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ═══ CODE SCREEN ═══ -->
<div class="code-screen" id="codeScreen">
  <h2>Prueba de Estadística</h2>
  <p>Ingresa el código de 3 cifras entregado por tu docente</p>
  <input class="code-in" id="codeIn" type="text" maxlength="3" placeholder="···" oninput="this.value=this.value.replace(/\D/g,'')" onkeydown="if(event.key==='Enter')verifyCode()">
  <div class="code-error" id="codeErr">Código incorrecto. Intenta de nuevo.</div>
  <button class="btn am" style="margin-bottom:16px" onclick="verifyCode()">Ingresar →</button>
  <button style="background:none;border:none;color:rgba(250,247,242,.4);font-size:.82rem;cursor:pointer" onclick="document.getElementById('codeScreen').classList.remove('show')">← Volver al contenido</button>
</div>


<!-- ═══ EXIT WARNING MODAL ═══ -->
<div class="warn-modal" id="warnModal">
  <div class="warn-box">
    <h2>⚠️ ¿Salir de la prueba?</h2>
    <p>Si sales o minimizas la página, <strong>la prueba se dará por finalizada</strong> y se registrarán las respuestas contestadas hasta este momento.</p>
    <div class="wb">
      <button class="btn" onclick="cancelExit()" style="background:#0b6464">Continuar prueba</button>
      <button class="btn rs" onclick="confirmExit()">Salir y registrar</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ═══ EXAM OVERLAY ═══ -->
<div class="overlay" id="testOverlay">
  <div style="background:var(--cream);border-radius:6px;max-width:880px;width:100%;max-height:94vh;overflow-y:auto" id="testScrollBox">
    <div class="test-wrap" id="testWrap"></div>
  </div>
</div>

<header>
  <h1>Esta<em>dística</em></h1>
  <p class="sub">Secuencia Didáctica · Grado 11° · Análisis de Datos</p>
  <div class="badge-row">
    <span class="badge">▸ 8 módulos</span>
    <span class="badge">▸ 5 actividades</span>
    <span class="badge">▸ 5 versiones de prueba</span>
    <span class="badge">▸ Panel docente</span>
  </div>
</header>

<nav id="mainNav">
  <a href="#porcentajes"><span class="n">00</span>Porcentajes</a>
  <a href="#poblacion"><span class="n">01</span>Población</a>
  <a href="#muestreo"><span class="n">02</span>Muestreo</a>
  <a href="#frecuencias"><span class="n">03</span>Frecuencias</a>
  <a href="#graficas"><span class="n">04</span>Gráficas</a>
  <a href="#medidas"><span class="n">05</span>Medidas</a>
  <a href="#actividades"><span class="n">06</span>Actividades</a>
  <a href="#pruebas"><span class="n">07</span>Prueba</a>
  <a href="#" onclick="openTeacherModal(event)" style="color:var(--amber-l)">👩‍🏫 Docente</a>
</nav>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════
     00 — PORCENTAJES
═══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section id="porcentajes">
<div class="container">
  <div class="sec-head">
    <div class="nn">00</div>
    <div><h2>Módulo de Porcentajes</h2><div class="divider"></div><p>Fundamento para el análisis estadístico</p></div>
  </div>
  <div class="def-box">
    <h4>¿Qué es un porcentaje?</h4>
    <p>Un <strong>porcentaje</strong> expresa una cantidad como fracción de 100. Es la herramienta clave para interpretar frecuencias relativas, tasas de cambio y proporciones en estadística. El símbolo <strong>%</strong> significa "de cada 100".</p>
  </div>
  <div class="fm">% = (Parte / Total) × 100 <small>· Parte = (% × Total) / 100 · Total = (Parte × 100) / %</small></div>

  <div class="g2" style="margin-top:22px">
    <div class="card hl">
      <h3>① ¿Qué % es A de B?</h3>
      <div class="row">
        <div><label class="lbl">Parte (A)</label><input class="inp inp-sm" id="p1a" type="number" placeholder="ej. 35"></div>
        <div><label class="lbl">Total (B)</label><input class="inp inp-sm" id="p1b" type="number" placeholder="ej. 140"></div>
      </div>
      <button class="btn" onclick="c1()">Calcular</button>
      <div class="res-box" id="r1">—</div>
    </div>
    <div class="card tl">
      <h3>② X% de N = ?</h3>
      <div class="row">
        <div><label class="lbl">Porcentaje %</label><input class="inp inp-sm" id="p2x" type="number" placeholder="ej. 15"></div>
        <div><label class="lbl">Total (N)</label><input class="inp inp-sm" id="p2n" type="number" placeholder="ej. 200"></div>
      </div>
      <button class="btn" onclick="c2()">Calcular</button>
      <div class="res-box" id="r2">—</div>
    </div>
    <div class="card rs">
      <h3>③ Total si A = X%</h3>
      <div class="row">
        <div><label class="lbl">Parte (A)</label><input class="inp inp-sm" id="p3a" type="number" placeholder="ej. 48"></div>
        <div><label class="lbl">%</label><input class="inp inp-sm" id="p3x" type="number" placeholder="ej. 30"></div>
      </div>
      <button class="btn" onclick="c3()">Calcular</button>
      <div class="res-box" id="r3">—</div>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <h3>④ Aumento / Descuento</h3>
      <div class="row">
        <div><label class="lbl">Valor inicial</label><input class="inp inp-sm" id="p4v" type="number" placeholder="ej. 80000"></div>
        <div><label class="lbl">% cambio</label><input class="inp inp-sm" id="p4c" type="number" placeholder="ej. 12"></div>
      </div>
      <div style="display:flex;gap:8px">
        <button class="btn" onclick="c4(1)">+ Aumento</button>
        <button class="btn am" onclick="c4(-1)">− Descuento</button>
      </div>
      <div class="res-box" id="r4">—</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ACTIVIDAD PORCENTAJES -->
  <div class="act" style="margin-top:32px">
    <div class="act-hd"><div class="act-num">P</div><h3>Actividad: Porcentajes en contexto real</h3></div>
    <button class="tog-c" onclick="toggleCalc('cpct')">🔬 Calculadora Científica</button>
    <div id="cpct" class="sci"></div>
    <div id="pct-q" class="q-area"><p>Haz clic en "Nuevo problema" para comenzar.</p></div>
    <div style="margin:12px 0;display:flex;gap:10px;flex-wrap:wrap">
      <button class="btn" onclick="genPct()">🎲 Nuevo problema</button>
      <button class="btn am" onclick="checkPct()">✔ Verificar</button>
    </div>
    <div id="pct-fb" class="fb"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="ex">
    <div class="ex-hd"><span class="etag">EJEMPLO 1</span><h4>Encuesta sobre transporte público</h4></div>
    <p>En una encuesta a 450 personas de Medellín, 288 usan transporte público diariamente. ¿Qué porcentaje usa transporte público?</p>
    <div class="step"><div class="sn">1</div><div class="sc"><b>Datos</b>Parte = 288 · Total = 450</div></div>
    <div class="step"><div class="sn">2</div><div class="sc"><b>Aplicar fórmula</b>% = (288/450) × 100 = 0.64 × 100 = <strong>64%</strong></div></div>
    <div class="step"><div class="sn">3</div><div class="sc"><b>Interpretar</b>El 64% de los encuestados depende del transporte público. El 36% restante usa otro medio.</div></div>
    <div class="fm">% = (288/450) × 100 = 64%</div>
  </div>
  <div class="ex">
    <div class="ex-hd"><span class="etag">EJEMPLO 2</span><h4>Variación porcentual de la canasta familiar</h4></div>
    <p>El precio promedio de la canasta familiar era $1 250 000 en enero y subió a $1 337 500 en diciembre. ¿Cuál fue la variación porcentual?</p>
    <div class="step"><div class="sn">1</div><div class="sc"><b>Variación absoluta</b>1 337 500 − 1 250 000 = $87 500</div></div>
    <div class="step"><div class="sn">2</div><div class="sc"><b>Variación porcentual</b>% = (87 500 / 1 250 000) × 100 = <strong>7%</strong></div></div>
    <div class="step"><div class="sn">3</div><div class="sc"><b>Interpretar</b>La canasta familiar aumentó un 7% en el año (tasa de inflación del hogar).</div></div>
  </div>
</div>
</section>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════
     01 — POBLACIÓN Y MUESTRA
═══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section id="poblacion">
<div class="container">
  <div class="sec-head"><div class="nn">01</div><div><h2>Población y Muestra</h2><div class="divider"></div><p>Conceptos fundamentales de la investigación estadística</p></div></div>
  <div class="g2">
    <div class="def-box"><h4>Población (N)</h4><p>Conjunto <strong>completo</strong> de individuos u objetos con una característica de interés. Un <strong>parámetro</strong> describe a la población (μ, σ, π).</p></div>
    <div class="def-box" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0b5252,#083838)"><h4>Muestra (n)</h4><p>Subconjunto <strong>representativo</strong> de la población. Un <strong>estadístico</strong> describe a la muestra (x̄, s, p̂). La validez del estudio depende de su selección.</p></div>
  </div>
  <div class="ex" style="margin-top:20px">
    <div class="ex-hd"><span class="etag">EJEMPLO REAL</span><h4>Estudio de consumo de redes sociales — DANE</h4></div>
    <p>El DANE quiere conocer cuántas horas diarias pasan los jóvenes de 15–25 años en redes sociales. Colombia tiene ≈ 8 200 000 jóvenes en ese rango.</p>
    <div class="step"><div class="sn">1</div><div class="sc"><b>Población (N)</b>Los 8 200 000 jóvenes colombianos de 15 a 25 años.</div></div>
    <div class="step"><div class="sn">2</div><div class="sc"><b>Muestra — Fórmula de Slovin (e = 3%)</b>n = 8 200 000 / (1 + 8 200 000 × 0.0009) ≈ <strong>1 111 personas</strong></div></div>
    <div class="step"><div class="sn">3</div><div class="sc"><b>Variable</b>Horas diarias en redes → Variable cuantitativa continua</div></div>
    <div class="step"><div class="sn">4</div><div class="sc"><b>Parámetro vs. Estadístico</b>Si la media real fuera μ = 4.2 h y la muestra da x̄ = 4.1 h, el estadístico estima bien el parámetro.</div></div>
  </div>
</div>
</section>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════
     02 — MUESTREO
═══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section id="muestreo">
<div class="container">
  <div class="sec-head"><div class="nn">02</div><div><h2>Técnicas de Muestreo</h2><div class="divider"></div><p>Métodos para seleccionar muestras representativas</p></div></div>
  <div class="g2">
    <div class="card hl"><h3>🎲 Aleatorio Simple</h3><p>Cada elemento tiene igual probabilidad. Se usa tabla de números aleatorios o software.</p></div>
    <div class="card tl"><h3>📋 Sistemático</h3><p>Se selecciona cada k-ésimo elemento (k = N/n). Inicio aleatorio entre 1 y k.</p></div>
    <div class="card rs"><h3>🗂 Estratificado</h3><p>Se divide en estratos homogéneos y se toma muestra proporcional de cada uno.</p></div>
    <div class="card"><h3>🔵 Conglomerados</h3><p>Se seleccionan grupos completos (barrios, colegios). Económico pero menos preciso.</p></div>
  </div>
  <div class="ex" style="margin-top:18px">
    <div class="ex-hd"><span class="etag">EJEMPLO — ESTRATIFICADO</span><h4>Encuesta de hábitos alimenticios</h4></div>
    <p>Un colegio tiene 720 estudiantes en tres jornadas. Se quiere encuestar 90 de forma estratificada.</p>
    <div class="tw"><table><thead><tr><th>Jornada</th><th>Estudiantes</th><th>Proporción</th><th>Muestra</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Mañana</td><td>360</td><td>50%</td><td>45</td></tr><tr><td>Tarde</td><td>252</td><td>35%</td><td>31</td></tr><tr><td>Noche</td><td>108</td><td>15%</td><td>14</td></tr></tbody><tfoot><tr><td>TOTAL</td><td>720</td><td>100%</td><td>90</td></tr></tfoot></table></div>
  </div>
</div>
</section>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════
     03 — TABLAS DE FRECUENCIA
═══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section id="frecuencias">
<div class="container">
  <div class="sec-head"><div class="nn">03</div><div><h2>Tablas de Frecuencia</h2><div class="divider"></div><p>Organización sistemática de datos reales</p></div></div>
  <div class="g2">
    <div class="def-box"><h4>Frecuencia Absoluta (fi)</h4><p>Número de veces que aparece cada valor. Σfi = n</p></div>
    <div class="def-box" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0b5252,#083838)"><h4>Frecuencia Relativa (hi)</h4><p>hi = fi / n. Proporción de cada valor. Σhi = 1</p></div>
    <div class="def-box" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#4d2a00,#2a1500)"><h4>Frecuencia Acumulada (Fi)</h4><p>Suma de fi hasta el valor i. Permite leer percentiles.</p></div>
    <div class="def-box" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#2a1a3a,#1a0a28)"><h4>Frec. Relativa Acumulada (Hi)</h4><p>Hi = Fi / n. El último valor es siempre 1 (100%).</p></div>
  </div>
  <div class="ex" style="margin-top:22px">
    <div class="ex-hd"><span class="etag">EJEMPLO — DATOS AGRUPADOS</span><h4>Tiempo de desplazamiento al colegio (minutos) — 50 estudiantes</h4></div>
    <p>Rango: 5 a 65 min. Sturges: k = 1 + 3.322×log(50) ≈ 7 clases, amplitud c ≈ 10 min.</p>
    <div class="tw"><table><thead><tr><th>Intervalo (min)</th><th>Marca xi</th><th>fi</th><th>hi</th><th>hi%</th><th>Fi</th><th>Hi%</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>[5–15)</td><td>10</td><td>6</td><td>0.12</td><td>12%</td><td>6</td><td>12%</td></tr><tr><td>[15–25)</td><td>20</td><td>12</td><td>0.24</td><td>24%</td><td>18</td><td>36%</td></tr><tr><td>[25–35)</td><td>30</td><td>15</td><td>0.30</td><td>30%</td><td>33</td><td>66%</td></tr><tr><td>[35–45)</td><td>40</td><td>10</td><td>0.20</td><td>20%</td><td>43</td><td>86%</td></tr><tr><td>[45–55)</td><td>50</td><td>5</td><td>0.10</td><td>10%</td><td>48</td><td>96%</td></tr><tr><td>[55–65]</td><td>60</td><td>2</td><td>0.04</td><td>4%</td><td>50</td><td>100%</td></tr></tbody><tfoot><tr><td>TOTAL</td><td>—</td><td>50</td><td>1.00</td><td>100%</td><td>—</td><td>—</td></tr></tfoot></table></div>
    <div class="step"><div class="sn">✓</div><div class="sc"><b>Interpretación</b>El 66% tarda menos de 35 minutos. Solo el 4% tarda más de 55 min. El intervalo modal es [25–35).</div></div>
  </div>
</div>
</section>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════
     04 — GRÁFICAS
